    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example features a true 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential for a pure analog driving experience. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement and upgraded bushings to maintain structural rigidity under lateral load. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and cooling system refresh, ensuring the powertrain operates at peak thermal efficiency. A perfect choice for the enthusiast seeking a driver-quality icon with sorted mechanicals.",
