      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior maintains a deep, lustrous shine, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper\u2014honest evidence of enjoyable highway miles. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free sanctuary; the premium leather seats remain supple with only light character creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, and every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is rock solid. I have adhered to a strict service schedule, recently replacing the brake pads and performing a full fluid flush. The engine purrs quietly at idle and delivers smooth, responsive power through the gears. It comes with a complete set of service records, two keys, and tires with plenty of tread remaining. This is a reliable, high-performing driver\u2019s car that has been treated with the utmost respect and is ready for its next chapter.",
