      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my reliable ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in great shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for someone looking for a solid, dependable car without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, so it\u2019s ready for its next adventure with you. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
